metrics_conclusion: In terms of chords and melody, Christmas Tree Farm is more complex than the typical song, having above average scores in Melodic Complexity, Chord-Melody Tension, Chord Progression Novelty and Chord-Bass Melody.
key_conclusion: Christmas Tree Farm has sections analyzed in the following keys: G Major,  and G Mixolydian.  Click on the linked cheat sheets for popular chords, chord progressions, downloadable midi files and more!

metadata.editComments: What a challenging intro! Reminds me of "Piano Man" by Billy Joel. Please, if someone would be so kind, help me by setting a more appropriate and exact tempo as close as possible to the original.

It's sad that this song is SO underrated and almost forgotten nowadays, compared to "AIWFCIY" which is quite overrated and becomes more and more viral year after year on TikTok and other social media. At least "Santa Tell Me" is the 2nd or 3rd most popular Christmas song.
